 <PERSON> Earleen </PERSON> <PERSON> Fisher </PERSON> is The <ORGANIZATION> Associated </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> Press </ORGANIZATION> bureau chief of <LOCATION> South </LOCATION> <LOCATION> Asia </LOCATION>, based in <LOCATION> New </LOCATION> <LOCATION> Delhi </LOCATION>. She has been in <LOCATION> Kabul </LOCATION> since March 22.
