last year, state authorities said <PERSON> Landy </PERSON>'s relationship with <PERSON> Wilson </PERSON> caused the singer `` severe emotional damage, psychological dependence and financial exploitation.'' <PERSON> Landy </PERSON>, who holds a doctorate in psychology from the <ORGANIZATION> University </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> of </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> Oklahoma </ORGANIZATION>, calls his methods `` 24-hour therapy,'' in which a therapist attempts to control every aspect of his patient's life.
</TEXT>
